title: MisterMusic Show 299 -new indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 299 (2 hours) 192kbps stereo



On This week's show -new music from Fujiya and Miyagi, Woods, Damien Jurado, Rare Monk, and another new track from the latest album by Kevin Drew.
The Oldie of the Week is a big hit that spent 3 weeks at number 1 on the US modern rock charts 20 years ago, in April 1994.

Plus a mix of new indie and alternative music and classic hits from over 5 decades of rock.



The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly, and heard globally on Rock XS Radio.

Thanks for listening-
